Doing glam for a destination wedding is not the same as local and here are 3 things I always do differently to make sure you look flawless, no matter the location 💍🌍

1️⃣ Climate-proof glam – I tailor your entire makeup routine based on the destination’s weather. Humid beach? Cold hills? I’ve got your skin covered.
2️⃣ Travel-tested kit – I carry everything, from backups to skin prep essentials, so we’re never caught off guard.
3️⃣ Timeline planning – I help you schedule the perfect glam time around your travel, events, and natural light — because your glow needs its moment ✨

When you’re traveling for love, your glam should travel with the same energy 💄💫
DM me if you’re planning a destination wedding ,let’s make magic, wherever you are!
